  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effects and safety of Anlotinib with placebo in
      patients with metastatic colorectal cancer refractory to standard chemotherapies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Anlotibib (AL3818) is a kind of innovative medicines approved by State Food and Drug
      Administration（SFDA:2011L00661） which was researched by Jiangsu Chia-tai Tianqing
      Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd.To compare the effects and safety of Anlotinib with placebo in
      patients with metastatic colorectal cancer refractory to standard chemotherapies.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
